                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>balči bī-hin šī yaʕni, amma uxṛa zād zararliyye xayyo. al-ḥayye al-wāḥad mā yimin min-he. </ANNOTATION_VALUE>
            </ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION>
        </ANNOTATION>
