                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>al-ḥayye yugḏ̣ub-ha b-īd-u gabəḷ-ma yiktil-ha yugḏ̣ub-ha b-īd-u, Aḥmad, mā yxāf min-ha.</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
